data.title: Enrique bunbury y vicentico
data.meta_description: Los Auténticos Decadentes, Enrique Bunbury, Carla Morrison, Café Tacvba, Vicentico, Natalia.
data.text:
Los Auténticos Decadentes, Enrique Bunbury, Carla Morrison, Café Tacvba, Vicentico, Natalia.

The famous songs had everyone dancing with their arms in the air, which he really seemed to appreciate, and played up to the audience, extending and repeating choruses of the most popular songs. Bunbury, Lafourcade, Morrison y Café Tacvba lideran Vive Latino 2016. When he first walked on stage, the audience was a see of bright lights radiating from smart phones taking videos, which usually bothers me throughout a performance, so it was great when Bunbury encouraged everyone to put them away saying ‘are you here to see me, or to tell the internet you’re seeing me’, which was cool! He opened the show with some tracks from Palosanto, the newest album, and sang a great combination of tracks from his newer and older work. His dance moves are also extremely entertaining as he interacts with his band members, and shouts at the audience to join in. The almost 50 years old artist has more energy and stage presence than I’ve seen from many artists half his age, and he commands the audiences attention from the moment he steps on the stage.īunbury has an incredible voice, and the way that he manipulates its rocky sound is original and refreshing. Con más de 30 años de historia dentro de la escena del rock del Cono Sur, al lado de su inseparable banda, Los Fabulosos Cadillacs y de manera solista el cantante ha conquistado múltiples países, poniendo a bailar a quien escuche sus canciones y ofreciendo grandes conciertos. En 2008, l'artiste sort un disque intitul Hellville de luxe. Hablar de Vicentico es sinónimo de música elegante y exquisita. Chaque fois, sortiront galement les albums live correspondants. Enrique Bunbury enregistrera ensuite des disques en collaboration avec diffrents artistes ainsi les albums Bushido, en 2003, et Bunbury & Vegas, en 2006. Enrique Ortiz de Landázuri Izarduy (Zaragoza, España, 11 de agosto de 1967), 1 más conocido como Enrique Bunbury o simplemente Bunbury, es un cantante, compositor y músico español.Es reconocido por haber sido el vocalista de la banda de rock Héroes del Silencio.
